Additional HCP terraform features : 

Health assessments : 
------------------
Terraform can automatically run health assessments on your workspaces once every 24hrs or so.
Checks for Drift detection.

Workspaces often depends on each other

Run triggers : 

HCP Terraform  > networking workspace >managed infra   
                    plan-> apply
                         |
                      Run Triggers
                      Queue a run
                      Firewall workspace


Benefits of run triggers :
- Run triggers let u connect a workspace to one or more source workspaces.
- HCP terraform automatically queues a run in the connected downstream workspace.
- Each workspace can connect to up to 20 source workspaces.
- Run triggers fires on successful applies in source workspaces and that they enable workspace-to-workspace automation.

